<L>__{interior hospital, kuwait, day}
<A>__{one more tug on the sheet and we see, and suddenly hear, from william starks' p.o.v. the chaos of the hospital around him as doctors and nurses tend as best as they can to the injured soldiers. our glimpse of starks reveals a red stretcher soaked in blood and the severe head wound where a bullet's minced his skull. then, slowly, steadily, a heartbeat is heard over the muffled sounds of the hospital and, as his pulse quickens, so does the pace of the world around him.}
